	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Game for the nes and famicom are the same so there is no special rewiring if you take a famicom game and put in inside a nes cart. As long the hardware (mapper) and board are identical, it will work. 
<br />
<br />I tested some nes game on my famicom dev board to make sure the dev cart is stable and had no issue.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


