<br />
<br />Connect the signals. CLK and the expansion pins don't go anywhere (unless you want expansion sound.) CIRAM = VRAM, PRG A# = A#, CHR A# = CA#, PRG /CE = /ROMSEL, etc. SOUND I connects to SOUND O...

		

